== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
[[File:This_Is_Us_(TV_series)_title_card.jpg|thumb]]
2015年9月2日，[[全國廣播公司|NBC]]預訂了由《[[外星鄰居|外星鄰居]]》、《[[遊俠笑傳|遊俠笑傳]]》主創[[丹·福吉爾曼|丹·福吉曼]]開創的新劇試播集，並由曾於電影《[[熟男型不型|熟男型不型]]》中合作過的{{link-en|約翰·瑞卡|John Requa}}與{{link-en|葛倫·費卡拉|Glenn Ficarra}}執導，三人也將與傑斯·羅森塔爾（{{lang|en|Jess Rosenthal}}）與查理·高葛拉克（{{lang|en|Charlie Gogolak}}）共同擔任執行製作，同時預計在年底展開拍攝。<ref name="Order Pilot">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/09/dan-fogelman-dramedy-nbc-pilot-order-focus-directors-1201512774/|title=Dan Fogelman Dramedy Gets Pilot Order At NBC With ‘Focus’ Duo Directing|author1=Nellie Andreeva|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-09-02|accessdate=2016-09-22|archive-date=2016-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604082102/http://deadline.com/2015/09/dan-fogelman-dramedy-nbc-pilot-order-focus-directors-1201512774/|dead-url=no}}</ref>本劇為福吉曼結束與{{link-en|ABC工作室|ABC Studios}}的合作後，和[[二十世紀福斯電視公司|二十世紀福斯電視公司]]展開四年新合約的首部作品。<ref name="Order Pilot"/>2016年5月12日，NBC宣布預訂《這就是我們》系列。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/dan-fogelman-dramedy-this-is-us-picked-up-to-series-by-nbc-1201754936/|title=Dan Fogelman Dramedy ‘This Is Us’ Picked Up To Series By NBC|author=Nellie Andreeva|work=Deadline|date=2016-05-12|accessdate=2016-09-22|archive-date=2016-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604040737/http://deadline.com/2016/05/dan-fogelman-dramedy-this-is-us-picked-up-to-series-by-nbc-1201754936/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2016/05/12/nbc-series-orders-2016-this-is-us-dramedy/|title=NBC Orders to Series ''This Is Us'' Dramedy From ''Grandfathered'' EP|author1=Rebecca Iannucci|publisher={{link-en|TVLine|TVLine}}|date=2016-05-12|accessdate=2016-09-22}}</ref>2016年9月27日，NBC宣布預訂全季18集集數。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/this-is-us-full-season-order-nbc-1201826545/|title=‘This Is Us’ Gets Full-Season Order At NBC For Total Of 18 Episodes|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline.com|date=2016-09-27|accessdate=2016-09-27|archive-date=2016-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928213342/http://deadline.com/2016/09/this-is-us-full-season-order-nbc-1201826545/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

